org.apache.logging.log4j.util

Class EnglishEnums

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.logging.log4j.util.EnglishEnums

  • public final class EnglishEnums
extends java.lang.Object
    Consider this class private.

    Helps convert English Strings to English Enum values.

    Enum name arguments are converted internally to upper case with the ENGLISH locale to avoid problems on the Turkish locale. Do not use with Turkish enum values.

        public static <T extends java.lang.Enum<T>> T valueOf(java.lang.Class<T> enumType,

        The name is converted internally to upper case with the ENGLISH locale to avoid problems on the Turkish locale. Do not use with Turkish enum values.
